|YKOEmotes are nonspoken social interactions between players. Most are
available to everyone. Guild emotes use the same targeting and message system,
but only active members of their guild can invoke them.

Use |YKBfeelings|YKO to list available emotes, |YKBfeelings guild|YKO to list
guild emotes, and |YKBsemote <emote>|YKO to preview one. The |YKBrandom|YKO
command chooses from the global and guild emotes currently available to you.

|WKBSee also: |YKBemoteapropos, feelings, guild emotes, random, semote|000
